msgid "The snippet above should render something like:"
msgstr "上面的代码片段渲染后应显示如下内容："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In Quarkus, it is also possible to define a <<type_safe_fragments,type-safe fragment>>."
