#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Create a UTF-8 encoded file located in the `src/main/resources/messages` directory of an application archive; e.g. `msg_de.properties`."
msgstr "在应用程序归档文件的 `src/main/resources/messages` 目录下创建一个 UTF-8 编码的文件；例如 `msg_de.properties` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "While a localized interface enables easy refactoring, an external file might be more convenient in many situations."
msgstr "虽然本地化界面便于重构，但在许多情况下，使用外部文件可能更为方便。"

#. type: Block title
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Localized Interface Example"
msgstr "界面本地化示例"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The value is the locale tag string (IETF)."
msgstr "该值为区域设置标识符字符串（IETF）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The value is the localized template."
msgstr "该值即为本地化后的模板。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Message bundle files must be encoded in _UTF-8_.\n"
"The file name consists of the relevant bundle name (e.g. `msg`) and underscore followed by a language tag (IETF; e.g. `en-US`).\n"
"The language tag may be omitted, in which case the language tag of the default bundle locale is used.\n"
"For example, if bundle `msg` has default locale `en`, then `msg.properties` is going to be treated as `msg_en.properties`."
msgstr "消息包文件必须采用 _UTF-8_ 编码。文件名由相应的包名称（例如 `msg` ）和下划线组成，后跟语言标签（IETF 标准；例如 `en-US` ）。 语言标签可以省略，此时将使用默认语言包的语言标签。例如，如果语言包 `msg` 的默认语言环境为 `en` ，则 `msg.properties` 将被视为 `msg_en.properties` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If there are multiple files for a specific locale then Qute attempts to resolve the ambiguity.\n"
"Localized files from the application root have higher priority and take precedence over localized files from dependencies.\n"
"If multiple files of the same priority exist, then the build fails.\n"
"For example, if the default bundle locale is `en` and the files `msg.properties` and `msg_en.properties` are found in the application root, then an exception is thrown and the build fails.\n"
"Or another example - if there are two dependencies and both contain the `msg_en.properties` file, then the build fails again.\n"
"On the other hand, if there is the `msg_en.properties` file in the application root and also the `msg_en.properties` file in a dependency, then messages from the application root take precedence and override the values from the dependency."
msgstr "如果某个特定语言环境存在多个文件，Qute 会尝试解决这种歧义。来自应用程序根目录的本地化文件优先级更高，优先于来自依赖项的本地化文件。如果存在多个优先级相同的文件，则构建会失败。 例如，如果默认包的区域设置为 `en` ，且在应用程序根目录中同时发现了 `msg.properties` 和 `msg_en.properties` 这两个文件，则会抛出异常并导致构建失败。再举一个例子——如果有两个依赖项，且两者都包含 `msg_en.properties` 文件，构建同样会失败。 另一方面，如果应用程序根目录中存在 `msg_en.properties` 文件，且某个依赖项中也存在 `msg_en.properties` 文件，则应用程序根目录中的消息具有优先级，并将覆盖来自依赖项的值。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The file format is very simple: each line represents either a key/value pair with the equals sign used as a separator or a comment (line starts with `#`).\n"
"Blank lines are ignored.\n"
"Keys are _mapped to method names_ from the corresponding message bundle interface.\n"
"Values represent the templates normally defined by `io.quarkus.qute.i18n.Message#value()`.\n"
"A value may be spread out across several adjacent normal lines.\n"
"In such case, the line terminator must be escaped with a backslash character `\\`.\n"
"The behavior is very similar to the behavior of the `java.util.Properties.load(Reader)` method."
msgstr "该文件格式非常简单：每行要么是一个以等号作为分隔符的键值对，要么是一条注释（行首以 `#` 开头）。空行将被忽略。 键会 _映射到_ 相应消息包接口中的 _方法名_ 。值通常由 `io.quarkus.qute.i18n.Message#value()` 定义的模板表示。一个值可能分布在几行相邻的普通行中。 在这种情况下，行结束符必须用反斜杠 `\\` 进行转义。其行为与 `java.util.Properties.load(Reader)` 方法的行为非常相似。"

#. type: Block title
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Localized File Example - `msg_de.properties`"
msgstr "本地化文件示例 - `msg_de.properties`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Each line in a localized file represents a key/value pair. The key must correspond to a method declared on the message bundle interface. The value is the message template."
msgstr "本地化文件中的每一行都代表一个键值对。键必须与消息包接口上声明的方法相对应。值即为消息模板。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Keys and values are separated by the equals sign."
msgstr "键和值之间用等号分隔。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We use the `.properties` suffix in our example because most IDEs and text editors support syntax highlighting of `.properties` files. But in fact, the suffix could be anything - it is just ignored."
msgstr "我们在示例中使用 `.properties` 后缀，是因为大多数 IDE 和文本编辑器都支持对 `.properties` 文件进行语法高亮显示。但实际上，后缀可以是任意名称——系统会直接忽略它。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "An example properties file is generated into the target directory for each message bundle interface automatically. For example, by default if no name is specified for `@MessageBundle` the file `target/qute-i18n-examples/msg.properties` is generated when the application is build via `mvn clean package`. You can use this file as a base for a specific locale. Just rename the file - e.g. `msg_fr.properties`, change the message templates and move it in the `src/main/resources/messages` directory."
msgstr "系统会为每个消息包接口自动在目标目录中生成一个示例属性文件。例如，默认情况下，如果未为 `@MessageBundle` 指定名称，则在通过 `mvn clean package` 构建应用程序时，会生成文件 `target/qute-i18n-examples/msg.properties` 。 您可以将此文件作为特定语言环境的基准文件。只需重命名该文件（例如 `msg_fr.properties` ），修改消息模板，然后将其移动到 `src/main/resources/messages` 目录中即可。"

#. type: Block title
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Value Spread Out Across Several Adjacent Lines"
msgstr "值分布在几行相邻的行中"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Note that the line terminator is escaped with a backslash character `\\` and white space at the start of the following line is ignored. I.e. `{msg:hello('Edgar')}` would be rendered as `Hello Edgar and good morning!`."
msgstr "请注意，行结束符需用反斜杠 `\\` 进行转义，且下一行开头的空格将被忽略。例如， `{msg:hello('Edgar')}` 将渲染为 `Hello Edgar 和 good morning!` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/qute-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
